fields.description:
Logging the full mail discussion as a comment each time makes the comments unreadable at the end.

As an alternative, we could log the last email answer as a comment and the rest of the discussion as an attachment.
fields.summary: Log as a comment only the last answer of an email thread and the rest of the discussion as an attachment
